      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_137_000017",
    "sentence": "德宗即位，征拜彭王傅。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_137_000018",
    "sentence": "建中三年，以疾卒，年八十，贈太子少師。",
    "entities": [
      {
